  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Maintenance Engineer (Satellite, RF, Network)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Maintenance Engineer (Satellite, RF, Network)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Involved in maintaining and supporting Satellite, Radio Frequency and Network Communication Systems.</strong></li>\n  <li>Responsible for troubleshooting Satellite, RF and Network System.</li>\n  <li>Managed integrated systems consisting of electrical, mechanical and electronic subsystems.</li>\n  <li>Involved in troubleshooting of Satellite Communication System, Frequency and baseband equipment using common engineering tools and support test equipment.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for Technical writing, testing and use of support test equipment.</li>\n  <li>Good in writing documentation, manual and instructions.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of Radio Frequency Engineering drawings or Electrical circuits.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Strong knowledge of Satellite, Radio Frequency and Network Communication Maintenance work.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Good in handling Satellite Communication system and Network Alcatel/Cisco Switches and Routers.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Good in Maintenance and Support work.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Involved in Network Communication System support and Satellite, RF Maintenance. </strong></li>\n  <li>Diploma in Engineering in Electrical/Electronics and Communication / Information Technology or equivalent.</li>\n  <li> Minimum 5 years of Satellite, Network and RF Maintenance and Support experience.</li>\n  <li>Standby/recall duties are required on the rotational basis</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p>\n<p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p>\n<p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
